description:
Excerpt from a Scandanavian piece on Lennie  featuring Lennie and Warne discussing Lennie's views on music and improvisation....more snippets to come.
Please see the Facebook page for the documentary called, Warne Marsh: An Improvised Life or follow us on Twitter at WarneMarshDoc 
Help us spread the word about this important American Artist and National Treasure.
